────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
- Team classification: Contender / Buyer / Neutral / Seller / Rebuilding
- Cap cleanup (cpuRosterCuts): releases lowest value-per-dollar players;
  protects X-Factor and OVR 88+ cornerstones
- CPU resign attempts: offer premium by team type (78%–110% of market)
- Competitive FA bidding engine: market-rate bids, cap-aware, need-weighted
- CPU incoming trade offers to user: getCpuTradeOffers() returns up to 3
  simultaneous offers per check; 35% chance gate prevents constant offer spam;
  claimedUserPlayerIds prevents two offers targeting the same player
- CPU-vs-CPU in-season trades: Weeks 2–8, capped at 2/week; 72% skip
  threshold for normal sellers (previously 60%) reduces news feed volume
- All 32 CPU teams have assigned schemes that affect sim ratings

